{
  "spec": {
    "title": "Soft Navigations and Interaction Contentful Paint",
    "url": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "get the current interaction context",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#get-the-current-interaction-context",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"get-the-current-interaction-context\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">get the current interaction context</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document③\">Document</a> <var>document</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>context</var> be the value of the internal <code class=\"highlight\">AsyncContext<c- p=\"\">.</c->Variable</code>\n <code class=\"highlight\"><c- p=\"\">[[</c->ActiveInteractionContext<c- p=\"\">]]</c-></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>context</var> is not null and <var>context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-context-document\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-context-document\">context document</a> is not equal\n to <var>document</var>, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>context</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "get the context for an interaction",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#get-the-context-for-an-interaction",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"get-the-context-for-an-interaction\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">get the context for an interaction</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document④\">Document</a> <var>document</var>, an\n  <var>interaction id</var>, and an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event\" id=\"ref-for-concept-event\">Event</a> <var>event</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#document-interaction-id-to-interaction-context\" id=\"ref-for-document-interaction-id-to-interaction-context\">interaction id to interaction context</a>[<var>interaction id</var>] <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists\">exists</a>,\n return <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#document-interaction-id-to-interaction-context\" id=\"ref-for-document-interaction-id-to-interaction-context①\">interaction id to interaction context</a>[<var>interaction id</var>].</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>interaction context</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-interactioncontext\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-interactioncontext\">InteractionContext</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-id\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-id\">id</a> to <var>interaction id</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-context-document\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-context-document①\">context document</a> to <var>document</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-start-time\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-start-time\">start time</a> to <var>event</var>’s <code class=\"highlight\">startTime</code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-set\" id=\"ref-for-map-set\">Set</a> <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#document-interaction-id-to-interaction-context\" id=\"ref-for-document-interaction-id-to-interaction-context②\">interaction id to interaction context</a>[<var>interaction id</var>] to\n <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "update the interaction contexts for an event",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#update-the-interaction-contexts-for-an-event",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"update-the-interaction-contexts-for-an-event\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">update the interaction contexts for an event</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document⑤\">Document</a> <var>document</var> and an\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event\" id=\"ref-for-concept-event①\">Event</a> <var>event</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>timestamp</var> be the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/hr-time/#dfn-current-high-resolution-time\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-current-high-resolution-time\">current high resolution time</a> given <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global\">relevant global object</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>is scroll</var> be true if <var>event</var>’s type is \"scroll\", and false otherwise.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>is input</var> be true if <var>event</var>’s type is an event type that would trigger\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/event-timing/#has-dispatched-input-event\" id=\"ref-for-has-dispatched-input-event\">has dispatched input event</a> (as defined in <a data-link-type=\"biblio\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#biblio-event-timing\" title=\"Event Timing API\">[EVENT-TIMING]</a>), and false otherwise.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>is scroll</var> is false and <var>is input</var> is false, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "For each <var>interaction context</var> of <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#document-interaction-id-to-interaction-context\" id=\"ref-for-document-interaction-id-to-interaction-context③\">interaction id to interaction context</a>’s\n values:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If <var>is scroll</var> is true and <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-scroll-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-scroll-timestamp\">first scroll timestamp</a>\n is unset:",
              "rationale": "set",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-scroll-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-scroll-timestamp①\">first scroll timestamp</a> to <var>timestamp</var>.</p>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var>is input</var> is true and <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-input-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-input-timestamp\">first input timestamp</a>\n is unset:",
              "rationale": "set",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-input-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-input-timestamp①\">first input timestamp</a> to <var>timestamp</var>.</p>"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "set the current interaction context for event dispatch",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#set-the-current-interaction-context-for-event-dispatch",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"set-the-current-interaction-context-for-event-dispatch\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">set the current interaction context for event dispatch</dfn> given null or a\n  <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/event-timing/#performanceeventtiming\" id=\"ref-for-performanceeventtiming\">PerformanceEventTiming</a></code> object <var>timingEntry</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>timingEntry</var> is null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>event</var> be <var>timingEntry</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://pr-preview.s3.amazonaws.com/mmocny/event-timing/pull/165.html#performanceeventtiming-associated-event\" id=\"ref-for-performanceeventtiming-associated-event\">associated event</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>interaction id</var> be <var>timingEntry</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/event-timing/#dom-performanceeventtiming-interactionid\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performanceeventtiming-interactionid\">interactionId</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>interaction id</var> is null or 0, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>document</var> be <var>event</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global①\">relevant global object</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-window\">associated Document</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#update-the-interaction-contexts-for-an-event\" id=\"ref-for-update-the-interaction-contexts-for-an-event\">Update the interaction contexts for an event</a> given <var>document</var> and <var>event</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>interaction context</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#get-the-context-for-an-interaction\" id=\"ref-for-get-the-context-for-an-interaction\">geting the context for an interaction</a> given\n <var>document</var>, <var>interaction id</var>, and <var>event</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set the value of the internal <code class=\"highlight\">AsyncContext<c- p=\"\">.</c->Variable</code> <code class=\"highlight\"><c- p=\"\">[[</c->ActiveInteractionContext<c- p=\"\">]]</c-></code> to\n <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "unset the current interaction context after event dispatch",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#unset-the-current-interaction-context-after-event-dispatch",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"unset-the-current-interaction-context-after-event-dispatch\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">unset the current interaction context after event dispatch</dfn>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Set the value of the internal <code class=\"highlight\">AsyncContext<c- p=\"\">.</c->Variable</code> <code class=\"highlight\"><c- p=\"\">[[</c->ActiveInteractionContext<c- p=\"\">]]</c-></code> to null.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "create an interaction contentful paint entry",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#create-an-interaction-contentful-paint-entry",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"create-an-interaction-contentful-paint-entry\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">create an interaction contentful paint entry</dfn>, given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#global-object\" id=\"ref-for-global-object②\">global object</a> <var>global</var>, an\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-interactioncontext\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-interactioncontext③\">InteractionContext</a> <var>interaction context</var>, a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largestcontentfulpaint\" id=\"ref-for-largestcontentfulpaint③\">LargestContentfulPaint</a></code> <var>lcpEntry</var>, and a\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-paint-timing-info③\">paint timing info</a> <var>paintTimingInfo</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>entry</var> be a new <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontentfulpaint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontentfulpaint④\">InteractionContentfulPaint</a></code> object in <var>global</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-global-object-realm\" id=\"ref-for-concept-global-object-realm\">realm</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>entry</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontentfulpaint-context\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontentfulpaint-context③\">context</a> to <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>entry</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontentfulpaint-largest-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontentfulpaint-largest-contentful-paint①\">largest contentful paint</a> to <var>lcpEntry</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>entry</var>’s associated <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-paint-timing-info④\">paint timing info</a> to <var>paintTimingInfo</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>entry</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "process a new attributed contentful paint candidate",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#process-a-new-attributed-contentful-paint-candidate",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"process-a-new-attributed-contentful-paint-candidate\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">process a new attributed contentful paint candidate</dfn> given a\n  <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largestcontentfulpaint\" id=\"ref-for-largestcontentfulpaint④\">LargestContentfulPaint</a></code> <var>lcpEntry</var>, a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document⑥\">Document</a> <var>document</var>, and an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-interactioncontext\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-interactioncontext④\">InteractionContext</a>\n  <var>interaction context</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-scroll-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-scroll-timestamp②\">first scroll timestamp</a> is set and\n <var>lcpEntry</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#dom-largestcontentfulpaint-rendertime\" id=\"ref-for-dom-largestcontentfulpaint-rendertime\">renderTime</a></code> is greater than <var>interaction context</var>’s\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-scroll-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-scroll-timestamp③\">first scroll timestamp</a>, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-input-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-input-timestamp②\">first input timestamp</a> is set and <var>lcpEntry</var>’s\n <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#dom-largestcontentfulpaint-rendertime\" id=\"ref-for-dom-largestcontentfulpaint-rendertime①\">renderTime</a></code> is greater than <var>interaction context</var>’s\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-input-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-input-timestamp③\">first input timestamp</a>, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>global</var> be <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global②\">relevant global object</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>paint timing info</var> be <var>lcpEntry</var>’s associated <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-paint-timing-info⑤\">paint timing info</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>icpEntry</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#create-an-interaction-contentful-paint-entry\" id=\"ref-for-create-an-interaction-contentful-paint-entry\">create an interaction contentful paint entry</a> given\n <var>global</var>, <var>interaction context</var>, <var>lcpEntry</var>, and <var>paint timing info</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\">Queue</a> <var>icpEntry</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Add <var>icpEntry</var> to <var>global</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-performance-entry-buffer\">performance entry buffer</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-contentful-paint\">first contentful paint</a> is null:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-contentful-paint①\">first contentful paint</a> to <var>icpEntry</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-largest-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-largest-contentful-paint\">largest contentful paint</a> to <var>icpEntry</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "evaluate soft navigation emission",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#evaluate-soft-navigation-emission",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"evaluate-soft-navigation-emission\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">evaluate soft navigation emission</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document⑦\">Document</a> <var>document</var> and an\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-interactioncontext\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-interactioncontext⑧\">InteractionContext</a> <var>interaction context</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-emitted\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-emitted\">emitted</a> is true, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#document-active-soft-navigation-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-document-active-soft-navigation-candidate\">active soft navigation candidate</a> is not <var>interaction context</var>, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-url-value\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-url-value①\">first URL value</a> is unset, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-contentful-paint②\">first contentful paint</a> is null, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>global</var> be <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global③\">relevant global object</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>entry</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#create-a-soft-navigation-entry\" id=\"ref-for-create-a-soft-navigation-entry\">create a soft navigation entry</a> given <var>global</var> and <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#emit-a-soft-navigation-entry\" id=\"ref-for-emit-a-soft-navigation-entry\">Emit a soft navigation entry</a> given <var>global</var> and <var>entry</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-emitted\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-emitted①\">emitted</a> to true.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "create a soft navigation entry",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#create-a-soft-navigation-entry",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"create-a-soft-navigation-entry\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">create a soft navigation entry</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#global-object\" id=\"ref-for-global-object③\">global object</a> <var>global</var>, and an\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-interactioncontext\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-interactioncontext⑨\">InteractionContext</a> <var>interaction context</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>entry</var> be a new <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#performancesoftnavigation\" id=\"ref-for-performancesoftnavigation③\">PerformanceSoftNavigation</a></code> object in <var>global</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-global-object-realm\" id=\"ref-for-concept-global-object-realm①\">realm</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>entry</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#performancesoftnavigation-context\" id=\"ref-for-performancesoftnavigation-context⑥\">context</a> to <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>first paint</var> be <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-contentful-paint③\">first contentful paint</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>first paint</var> is not null:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>entry</var>’s associated <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-paint-timing-info⑦\">paint timing info</a> to <var>first paint</var>’s associated <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-paint-timing-info⑧\">paint timing info</a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>entry</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "emit a soft navigation entry",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#emit-a-soft-navigation-entry",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"emit-a-soft-navigation-entry\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">emit a soft navigation entry</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#global-object\" id=\"ref-for-global-object④\">global object</a> <var>global</var> and a\n  <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#performancesoftnavigation\" id=\"ref-for-performancesoftnavigation④\">PerformanceSoftNavigation</a></code> <var>entry</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>entry</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#performanceentry-navigation-id\" id=\"ref-for-performanceentry-navigation-id\">navigation id</a> to <var>entry</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#dom-performancesoftnavigation-interactionid\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancesoftnavigation-interactionid①\">interactionId</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>global</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#global-object-current-navigation-id\" id=\"ref-for-global-object-current-navigation-id\">current navigation id</a> to <var>entry</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#dom-performancesoftnavigation-interactionid\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancesoftnavigation-interactionid②\">interactionId</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-queue-a-performanceentry②\">Queue</a> <var>entry</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Add <var>entry</var> to <var>global</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-performance-entry-buffer①\">performance entry buffer</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "process a same document commit",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#process-a-same-document-commit",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"process-a-same-document-commit\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">process a same document commit</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document⑧\">Document</a> <var>document</var>, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#string\" id=\"ref-for-string\">string</a> <var>url</var>,\n  and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#string\" id=\"ref-for-string①\">string</a> <var>navigation type</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>url</var> is equal to <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document-url\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-url\">url</a>, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>interaction context</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#get-the-current-interaction-context\" id=\"ref-for-get-the-current-interaction-context\">getting the current interaction context</a> given\n <var>document</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>interaction context</var> is null, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-last-url-value\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-last-url-value\">last URL value</a> to <var>url</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-url-update-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-url-update-timestamp\">first URL update timestamp</a> is unset:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-url-update-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-url-update-timestamp①\">first URL update timestamp</a> to the\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/hr-time/#dfn-current-high-resolution-time\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-current-high-resolution-time①\">current high resolution time</a> given <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global④\">relevant global object</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-first-url-value\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-first-url-value②\">first URL value</a> to <var>url</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-navigation-type\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-navigation-type①\">navigation type</a> to <var>navigation type</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#document-active-soft-navigation-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-document-active-soft-navigation-candidate①\">active soft navigation candidate</a> to <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#evaluate-soft-navigation-emission\" id=\"ref-for-evaluate-soft-navigation-emission\">Evaluate soft navigation emission</a> given <var>document</var> and <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "get the next interactionId",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#get-the-next-interactionid",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"get-the-next-interactionid\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">get the next interactionId</dfn> for a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window\" id=\"ref-for-window\">Window</a></code> <var>window</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>window</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://pr-preview.s3.amazonaws.com/mmocny/event-timing/pull/165.html#window-interaction-count\" id=\"ref-for-window-interaction-count\">interaction count</a> to <var>window</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://pr-preview.s3.amazonaws.com/mmocny/event-timing/pull/165.html#window-interaction-count\" id=\"ref-for-window-interaction-count①\">interaction count</a> plus 1.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>window</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://pr-preview.s3.amazonaws.com/mmocny/event-timing/pull/165.html#window-initial-interactionid-value\" id=\"ref-for-window-initial-interactionid-value①\">initial interactionId value</a> plus (<var>window</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://pr-preview.s3.amazonaws.com/mmocny/event-timing/pull/165.html#window-interaction-count\" id=\"ref-for-window-interaction-count②\">interaction count</a>\n times <var>window</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://pr-preview.s3.amazonaws.com/mmocny/event-timing/pull/165.html#window-interactionid-increment\" id=\"ref-for-window-interactionid-increment\">interactionId increment</a>).</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "additions to DOM event dispatch",
      "html": "In the modifications to the DOM specification’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-dispatch\" id=\"ref-for-concept-event-dispatch\">event dispatch</a> algorithm defined in <a data-link-type=\"biblio\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#biblio-event-timing\" title=\"Event Timing API\">[EVENT-TIMING]</a>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "Right after the step that sets <var>timingEntry</var> to the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://pr-preview.s3.amazonaws.com/mmocny/event-timing/pull/165.html#initialize-and-record-event-timing-processing-start\" id=\"ref-for-initialize-and-record-event-timing-processing-start\">initialize and record event timing processing start</a>, run the following step:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#set-the-current-interaction-context-for-event-dispatch\" id=\"ref-for-set-the-current-interaction-context-for-event-dispatch\">Set the current interaction context for event dispatch</a> given <var>timingEntry</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Right before the step that calls <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://pr-preview.s3.amazonaws.com/mmocny/event-timing/pull/165.html#record-event-timing-processing-end\" id=\"ref-for-record-event-timing-processing-end\">record event timing processing end</a>, run the following step:",
          "rationale": "unset",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#unset-the-current-interaction-context-after-event-dispatch\" id=\"ref-for-unset-the-current-interaction-context-after-event-dispatch\">Unset the current interaction context after event dispatch</a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "additions to report largest contentful paint",
      "html": "In <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#report-largest-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-report-largest-contentful-paint\">report largest contentful paint</a>, let <var>candidates</var> be the union of the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#list-of-painted-images\" id=\"ref-for-list-of-painted-images\">list of painted images</a>\n  and the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#list-of-painted-text\" id=\"ref-for-list-of-painted-text\">list of painted text</a>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>contextToNewLargestCandidate</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-map\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-map①\">map</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "For each <var>candidate</var> in <var>candidates</var>:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>element</var> be <var>candidate</var>’s element.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>element</var> is null, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>interaction context</var> be <var>element</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#node-associated-interaction-context\" id=\"ref-for-node-associated-interaction-context\">associated interaction context</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>interaction context</var> is null, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>size</var> be <var>candidate</var>’s size.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-largest-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-largest-contentful-paint②\">largest contentful paint</a> is not null and\n <var>size</var> is less than or equal to <var>interaction context</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#interactioncontext-largest-contentful-paint\" id=\"ref-for-interactioncontext-largest-contentful-paint③\">largest contentful paint</a>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#dom-interactioncontentfulpaint-largestcontentfulpaint\" id=\"ref-for-dom-interactioncontentfulpaint-largestcontentfulpaint①\">largestContentfulPaint</a></code>’s\n <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#dom-largestcontentfulpaint-size\" id=\"ref-for-dom-largestcontentfulpaint-size\">size</a></code>, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var>contextToNewLargestCandidate</var>[<var>interaction context</var>] is unset or <var>size</var> is greater than\n <var>contextToNewLargestCandidate</var>[<var>interaction context</var>]'s size:",
              "rationale": "set",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-set\" id=\"ref-for-map-set①\">Set</a> <var>contextToNewLargestCandidate</var>[<var>interaction context</var>] to <var>candidate</var>.</p>"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "For each <var>interaction context</var> → <var>newLcpCandidate</var> in <var>contextToNewLargestCandidate</var>:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>newLcpEntry</var> be the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/largest-contentful-paint/#largestcontentfulpaint\" id=\"ref-for-largestcontentfulpaint⑤\">LargestContentfulPaint</a></code> entry representing <var>newLcpCandidate</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#process-a-new-attributed-contentful-paint-candidate\" id=\"ref-for-process-a-new-attributed-contentful-paint-candidate\">Process a new attributed contentful paint candidate</a> given <var>newLcpEntry</var>, <var>document</var>, and\n <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#evaluate-soft-navigation-emission\" id=\"ref-for-evaluate-soft-navigation-emission①\">Evaluate soft navigation emission</a> given <var>document</var> and <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "additions to node insert",
      "html": "Run the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>document</var> be the node’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-node-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-node-document\">node document</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>interaction context</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#get-the-current-interaction-context\" id=\"ref-for-get-the-current-interaction-context①\">getting the current interaction context</a> given\n <var>document</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>interaction context</var> is not null:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Set the node’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#node-associated-interaction-context\" id=\"ref-for-node-associated-interaction-context①\">associated interaction context</a> to <var>interaction context</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Designate the node as a <strong>container root</strong> (as defined in <a data-link-type=\"biblio\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#biblio-container-timing\" title=\"Container Timing API\">[CONTAINER-TIMING]</a>).</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>For the node and each of its descendants, remove them from the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document①③\">Document</a>’s\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#previously-reported-paints\" id=\"ref-for-previously-reported-paints\">previously reported paints</a> (as defined in <a data-link-type=\"biblio\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#biblio-paint-timing\" title=\"Paint Timing\">[PAINT-TIMING]</a>).</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "In <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-queue-a-performanceentry③\">queue a PerformanceEntry</a>, after step 1 (initializing the entry), add the following steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If <var>newEntry</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#performanceentry-navigation-id\" id=\"ref-for-performanceentry-navigation-id②\">navigation id</a> is 0:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>newEntry</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#performanceentry-navigation-id\" id=\"ref-for-performanceentry-navigation-id③\">navigation id</a> to <var>global</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/soft-navigations/#global-object-current-navigation-id\" id=\"ref-for-global-object-current-navigation-id③\">current navigation id</a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}